      "content": "it's more than just feeling pressure though. it feels like being stuck in a burning building and people are telling you to just relax and enjoy the view. like, if the whole system is collapsing and there's no real hope for a stable future, doesn't it just feel like the only logical thing left is to just... stop? to opt out before it all gets even worse?",
